###Configuration Change Logging(makuha lahat ng mga tinatype sa device)
config t
archive
log config
logging enable
notify syslog


###Failed Login Attempts(isntant log attemps)
config t
longin on-failure log
login on-success log


###this is to block ping and ssh(you will gets logs or message like denied or ip accesslogp is denied)
config t
access-list 100 deny ip any host 208.8.8.189 log
access-list 100 permit ip any any
interface GigabitEthernet0/0
ip access-group 100 in


###get back the ping and able to ssh again
config t
interface GigabitEthernet0/0
no ip access-group 100 in
end




